    dc:creator "Perger, Robert; Guerra, Fernando" ;
    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "The first longhorned beetle record for the Prepuna in the Bolivian Andes and Potosi Department in Bolivia: a new species of Dirocoremia (Coleoptera: Cerambycidae: Rhopalophorini)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235584>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235585>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235586>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235587> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235584>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A, map of Bolivia, (a) study area, Tupiza, Potosi department; B, habitat of Dirocoremia tupizai sp. n." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/235584/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235585>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Dirocoremia tupizai sp. n., holotype male (CBF); A, habitus dorsal, scale bar 2 mm; B, head and pronotum dorsal, scale bar 1 mm; C, head; D, prothorax ventral; scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/235585/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235586>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A, Coremia bruchi (Gounelle, 1905), holotype male, Argentina, Tucuman prov., Tapia, 600 m, G. A. Baer leg., 3 - 4 1903, BMNH (E) 1269328 (BMNH); B, Dirocoremia ingae (Marques, 1994), paratype male, Brazil, Sâo Paulo, ltu, 13. XI. 1960, U. Martins leg. (MZSP)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/235586/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235587>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Metatibia, lateral, A, Dirocoremia bruchi, male, Entre Rios, Argentina (WH); B, D. tupizai sp. n., paratype male (CBF) (arrow indicating constriction)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/235587/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

